.../dkb-1.0/docs/...

This directory contains documentation files for the dkb system. They are all in
SunOS -man format. See the Sun manual `Formatting Documents'. The entire
documentation can be produced by typing `make'. The file `man.tr' will
then contain documentation in troff(1) format. To produce text-file output
(with no fancy formatting codes) type `make pr' instead. The file `man.tx'
will then contain sn spproximation of the documents which can be produced on
a line printer.

